10:18.776 --> 10:20.235
We are beyond
blotting and rubbing.

10:20.318 --> 10:22.864
We've moved on to sweating and crying.
Okay. Let's not panic.

10:22.947 --> 10:25.825
We'll tell Amelia what happened,
and then we'll pay to have it cleaned.

10:25.910 --> 10:28.663
What if it can't be cleaned, Mitchell?
Okay, okay.

10:28.746 --> 10:30.373
Then we'll pay for a new rug.

10:30.456 --> 10:31.624
Are you insane?

10:31.708 --> 10:35.588
This is a limited edition
alpaca handmade Stark rug.

10:35.671 --> 10:38.509
I saw it in Architectural Digest.
It costs $50,000.

10:38.591 --> 10:40.635
It was in Diane Keaton's house.
Oh, my-

10:40.719 --> 10:42.680
Oh, no. It was in-
oh, what's-her-name's house.

10:42.764 --> 10:44.515
Um, from Prizzi's Honor.

10:44.598 --> 10:48.020
From, uh-
Oh, she was in Addams Family.

10:48.103 --> 10:50.814
Anjelica Huston!
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.

10:50.897 --> 10:52.901
Oh, my God.
$50,000?

10:52.984 --> 10:55.571
For a rug? Cam, we don't
have that kind of money.

10:55.696 --> 10:59.617
Maybe she won't make us pay. I mean, we wouldn't
make someone pay if this happened to us.

10:59.701 --> 11:03.999
Did you not hear her on the phone?
“Fix it! Replace it! Write me a check!"

11:04.082 --> 11:06.251
