11:12.382 --> 11:14.761
No. I mean the rug.
Maybe we can turn the whole rug around.

11:14.844 --> 11:17.806
Put it under the couch. See?
No one would ever know it's there.

11:17.889 --> 11:20.935
Well, we would know.
Well-

11:23.480 --> 11:25.817
What are you thinking?
You don't wanna know.

11:25.900 --> 11:28.653
No, tell me, 'cause I think
I'm thinking the same thing.

11:28.736 --> 11:31.824
I seriously doubt that, because now I'm
