12:16.170 --> 12:18.632
maybe even taste my cupcakes,

12:18.715 --> 12:20.383
I will join you.

12:20.466 --> 12:23.720
No. Uh- No. No.
I am so confused right now.

12:23.805 --> 12:26.058
