12:37.238 --> 12:40.408
Yeah. That's what I'm talking about.

12:40.492 --> 12:43.203
Can I use your computer?
I just need to check one e-mail.

12:43.328 --> 12:46.582
Yeah, the kitchen. Gloria, I just
switched us to the next flight.

12:46.667 --> 12:48.459
Did you guys get everything
straightened out?

12:48.544 --> 12:52.424
