to the worst part of it yet.

14:26.081 --> 14:27.831
Which is?

14:27.916 --> 14:29.751
They're gonna
want to talk about it.

14:29.835 --> 14:32.547
Maybe not.

14:32.630 --> 14:35.342
Are you kidding?
Their parents never talked about anything,

14:35.425 --> 14:37.469
so they want to talk about everything.

14:37.554 --> 14:41.306
