15:09.509 --> 15:11.929
You could have made sure that I was okay.
Wanna talk about it?

15:12.012 --> 15:13.680
Yes.
Fine!

15:13.764 --> 15:17.352
Your mother and I were watching
a particularly racy episode of Hart to Hart.

15:17.477 --> 15:20.272
Oh! Stefanie Powers had to go
undercover as a call girl.

15:20.355 --> 15:21.858
Mm-mmm. Dad-
Hang on.

15:21.940 --> 15:23.692
This whole story makes
more sense- Okay.

15:23.776 --> 15:25.778
If you know I got a thing
for thigh-high boots.

15:25.863 --> 15:28.364
Oh, gross. Gross.
You are ruining sex for me.

15:28.448 --> 15:29.659
And boots.

15:29.742 --> 15:30.909
Hey.

15:32.077 --> 15:34.748
Working okay for you?
Yes.

15:34.832 --> 15:37.294
