to my brother in Colombia.

15:37.377 --> 15:40.631
- Oh.
- I was telling him about Claire.

15:40.714 --> 15:44.636
You know, I realized
there's so much I don't know about her.

15:44.719 --> 15:48.182
Like, for example,
what is her favorite word?

15:48.264 --> 15:51.602
Or what was
her first pet's name?

15:51.686 --> 15:53.813
Gloria, I'm not an idiot.

15:53.896 --> 15:55.690
Are you trying to get
Claire's password?

15:55.775 --> 15:58.486
[Sighs]
Okay, fine.

15:58.569 --> 16:00.363
I sent her something by mistake.

16:00.446 --> 16:04.118
I need to get into Claire's e-mail
to erase it before she sees it.

16:04.201 --> 16:06.704
- Before I see what?
- Hola, Claire.

16:06.787 --> 16:09.499
Hi, Gloria.
Before I see what?

16:09.582 --> 16:12.087
It's so embarrassing.

16:12.169 --> 16:14.798
[Sighs]
You see, Jay and I-

16:14.880 --> 16:17.175
it's a naked picture of Gloria.

16:17.258 --> 16:18.886
Whoa.

16:18.968 --> 16:21.723
Yes. Naked.

16:21.806 --> 16:24.017
- Mmm.
- I was gonna send it to Jay.

16:24.100 --> 16:26.729
You see everything-
the whole body.

16:26.812 --> 16:29.024
I need to sit.
Okay.

16:29.107 --> 16:30.942
Wow, Dad.

16:31.025 --> 16:35.990
So you just got done giving me a lecture on
the importance of locking my bedroom door...

16:36.073 --> 16:41.915
while in my house to retrieve naked pictures
that your wife accidentally sent me.

16:41.998 --> 16:45.919
