Mmm. Mmm.

16:46.003 --> 16:47.462
Wow.
What are you doing?

16:47.547 --> 16:50.341
- What I'm doing is deleting it.
- [ Phil] Good for you.

16:50.426 --> 16:53.428
Let's go to Vegas!
[ Gloria ] Ciao!

16:53.511 --> 16:55.305
Do us a favor. No pictures.

16:55.390 --> 16:57.433
Oh, Gloria. Listen.

16:57.516 --> 17:00.478
We do need to talk about the bake sale
at some point. I have some concerns.

17:00.563 --> 17:02.231
Of course you do.
Bye-bye!

17:02.314 --> 17:06.862
