this situation the wrong way,

17:09.489 --> 17:11.660
but I'm 80% sure
you're coming on to me.

17:13.287 --> 17:15.749
Okay, now 40.

17:15.830 --> 17:17.876
Mitchell, we need
to make a decision.

17:19.837 --> 17:22.130
It was the perfect plan.
Turn the rug,

17:22.214 --> 17:24.592
and she wouldn't find
the stain for years.

17:24.675 --> 17:27.471
But we couldn't do it.
We're too honest.

17:27.553 --> 17:30.600
There are certain moments
in life that define you,

17:30.683 --> 17:32.517
and this is
one of those moments.

17:32.602 --> 17:33.978
[ Footsteps ]

17:34.062 --> 17:37.441
[ Sighs ] Guys, I'm so
sorry that took so long.

17:37.525 --> 17:39.902
Oh, my God.
What happened here?

